  <brief_title>Sex Hormones and Pericardial Adipose Tissue</brief_title>
  <official_title>Do Endogenous Sex Hormones Affect Pericardial Adipose Tissue Volume of Males in The Multi-Ethnic Study of Atherosclerosis (MESA)?</official_title>
