  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study, our aim is to show the relation between sex hormones and PAT and to confirm
      whether PAT is associated with coronary artery calcification (CAC) in different testosterone
      levels in the males.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
